                        <p>“He’s a guy with a great work ethic who has the ability to make the guys around him better,” Lewis said of himself when asked how he would describe his strengths to an NFL general manager. “He is a team player, a hard worker, and he is a leader. He’s going to give you everything he has.  </p>
<p>“If you make that investment in me, I’ll make sure you’ve made the right investment.”</p>

